        </tr></tbody></table><h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="en-US" id="toc-id-24">Roteer figure</h2>

    <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="Body-no-indent">Wanneer ’n figuur
